entries.femaleVariant: Hey. Gig's all set up super sweet, like. Tonight, at the Red Dirt.
Talked to Kerry? Didn't change his mind or anything?
Haven't seen him like this since the Silverhand days.
No, no, not at all. He's pretty stoked, in fact.
Couldn't get Denny to come around?
What about Henry? Still not on board?
Nope. Tried my damndest, but no.
And don't worry about your axe. Got the gear all rounded up.
Didn't even try. Not wastin' my breath on that dicktip.
